  "title": "Customer Service Executive (Semiconductor)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Mon to Fri, 9am-6pm</p></li><li><p>Basic up $3500</p></li><li><p>Performance Bonus + Quarterly Bonus</p></li><li><p>Location: Kallang (Walkable distance from Lavender MRT)<br /> </p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibility:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Develop</strong> and <strong>nurture</strong> customer relationships through <strong>regular communication</strong> to understand their needs and promote <strong>long-term loyalty</strong> and <strong>engagement</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Address and <strong>resolve</strong> customer <strong>inquiries</strong> promptly and effectively.</p></li><li><p>Provide <strong>accurate quotations</strong> to customers.</p></li><li><p>Investigate and <strong>resolve customer complaints</strong>, ensuring timely and satisfactory <strong>feedback</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Ensure efficient <strong>processing</strong> and <strong>delivery</strong> of customer orders.</p></li><li><p>Maintain <strong>accurate</strong> and up-to-date <strong>customer records</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Generate <strong>reports</strong> for management on <strong>customer satisfaction</strong>, <strong>issue resolution</strong>, and <strong>feedback</strong> to support improvements in customer relations strategies, as well as <strong>sales forecasts</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with <strong>sales</strong>, <strong>marketing</strong>, <strong>operations</strong>, and <strong>purchasing</strong> departments to strengthen customer relationships.</p></li><li><p><strong>Travel internationally</strong> for <strong>exhibitions</strong> as required.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lead</strong> the establishment of a <strong>customer relations team</strong> as the business grows.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Min Diploma </strong>or higher in <strong>Business</strong> or an equivalent field is required.</p></li><li><p><strong>1 to 2 years</strong> of relevant working experience.</p></li></ul><p>Interested Applicants, kindly send your updated CV to <a href=\"tel:+65 8500 3939\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">+65 8500 3939</a> or click on <em><strong>“APPLY NOW”.</strong></em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em><br /></p><p>EA License No: 15C7752<br />EA Personnel No: R22107485<br />EA Personnel Name: Chin Jia Hui, Janice</p>",
